content: It is very beautiful. And in my opinion, this is the best tarot app.

I love this app. Easy to use, visually stunning and a highly recommended accompaniment to the actual physical deck. The artwork by Ciro Marchetti is breathtaking. The app itself fins smoothly and is a pleasure to work with. 5 stars.
Lobe the app, its easy to navigate. Love the reverse interperetation that are included.
Love these, wish I could get the cards

Phenomenal deck. A picky person about tarot decks gives 5 stars lol. It is just the right amount of weight without being super heavy. The artwork really captures the essence of each card for me, making it easy to read. I was so glad they mass market released a physical deck that wasn't 200 dollars like the original collector's edition. I have had this app and been using it for a long time, and finally have a companion "in my hands" deck to go with it. I use both. Thank you thank you.
Love this deck! It is my favorite Cirro.
This is a great app. I own the physical deck, and love it. I'm very happy to have it in my mobile and tablet so I can use it anywhere. All of Ciro Marchetti's decks are spectacular.
